Ed,<br><br>
No talk is cheap or silly. It is all an important and profound part of the process. You do yourself an injustice. I listen to all your words. ...........and don't you dare call me a fool, or something, for hearing them! <br><br>
I have ghosts. We coexist because I honor them. They are the unburied. The time is too far past to put them to rest in the traditional way, so we still live together, in my mind. For better or for worse, and maybe they honor me by their presence, as well. Sometimes, I think they are better friends than most. I wondered once what it would be like to join them. For them, and myself, though, I know I am better off just where I am, with my BOC here in the here and now. If I do not exist, where would my ghosts wind up? Not in a very nice place, I bet!<br><br>
I salute you, my BOC.<br><br>
Art    
